<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-3D038F77-257D-4F68-B42B-71E70844B46F" version="1" lang="en-US"?><reference xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-3D038F77-257D-4F68-B42B-71E70844B46F" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic reference)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c reference oceReference-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic       reference/reference "><title class="- topic/title ">19 Winding options</title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="GUID-24D550D7-7054-4B6D-83E3-EC11A87279FE"><p class="- topic/p ">For the <ph class="- topic/ph " varid="productname">Colorado M-Series</ph> there are several winding options depending on the type of media you are using.</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Functional description</category></metadata></prolog><refbody class="- topic/body        reference/refbody "><section id="GUID-B3031E52-E8C8-4AD7-9379-D18B5359AC10" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Overview</title><p class="- topic/p ">In a media profile a media category is used that corresponds with the loaded media type. Each media category uses default media settings. One of the media settings is <ph translate="no" class="- topic/ph "><uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Winding tension</uicontrol></ph> that controls the winding tension that best fits the media type.</p><table id="GUID-D69A6861-D82B-486B-BC19-9426328400D8" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="4" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="25*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="25*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="20*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col4" colnum="4" colwidth="30*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Options</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Media category</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><ph translate="no" class="- topic/ph "><uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Tight winding</uicontrol></ph> value</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Media characteristics</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="19FUNC030" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-185DF587-7FB8-49A8-8BF3-626091680E7F.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 19 Print and wind without a tension bar?>19 Print and wind without a tension bar</xref></p><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="19FUNC060" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-F9E89CD5-31DA-4B47-B08E-B837C38B21C2.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 19 Print without winding?>19 Print without winding</xref></p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><ph translate="no" class="- topic/ph ">Polymeric &amp; cast vinyl</ph></p><p class="- topic/p "><ph translate="no" class="- topic/ph ">Monomeric vinyl</ph></p><p class="- topic/p "><ph translate="no" class="- topic/ph ">Film</ph></p><p class="- topic/p "><ph translate="no" class="- topic/ph ">Light paper</ph></p><p class="- topic/p "><ph translate="no" class="- topic/ph ">Paper</ph></p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><ph class="- topic/ph "><uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">no tension bar</uicontrol></ph></p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">The media can be transported well and is not too weak.</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="19FUNC040" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-BF953262-8898-4AFC-B545-338FAC9B091E.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 19 Print and wind with a tension bar?>19 Print and wind with a tension bar</xref></p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><ph translate="no" class="- topic/ph ">Heavy banner</ph></p><p class="- topic/p "><ph translate="no" class="- topic/ph ">Light banner</ph></p><p class="- topic/p "><ph translate="no" class="- topic/ph ">Textile</ph></p><p class="- topic/p "><ph translate="no" class="- topic/ph ">Canvas</ph></p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><ph class="- topic/ph "><uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">tension bar</uicontrol></ph></p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">The media is weaker and sensitive for buckling, but not too stiff.</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="19FUNC050" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-B5C11BED-C928-4685-96AE-0B0949CC35A9.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 19 Print and wind with a locked tension bar?>19 Print and wind with a locked tension bar</xref></p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><ph translate="no" class="- topic/ph ">Thick film</ph></p><p class="- topic/p "><ph translate="no" class="- topic/ph ">Heavy paper</ph></p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><ph class="- topic/ph "><uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">locked tension bar</uicontrol></ph></p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">The media is stiff.</p></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></refbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-77E3E148-DF16-4838-9432-CE905B393B0C.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Functional description</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
